                  Electrical Engineering with the Tandon School of
                  Engineering</a></div>
                <div class="col-xs-4">dual degree</div>
              </div>

              <p class="bold heading">Student Spotlight</p>
              <p>Our undergraduate students contribute greatly to the vitality
              of the department. The <a href="/home/undergrad/spotlight.html">Student
                Spotlight</a>, which is updated throughout the year, highlights
              exciting new research projects, course information, and student
              experiences.</p>

